result.notes:
Pressure (Depth), Temperature and Conductivity (CTD) profiles collected on 
Cefas (or DFR) plankton research cruises. The data in this archive broadly 
cover the European Shelf. Output files are varied in data format according to 
the collection system used and the level of post-processing carried out.
